text: Emmanuel Bunoz (born 15 May 1970) is a French rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:French male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
